________________________________________________________________________________________

|                                                                                        |

|         Install Ubuntu

|

|         Run The Following command For sound problem:-

|________________________________________________________________________________________

|

|         nano $PREFIX/etc/pulse/default.pa

|

|         Add the following line in the last on the file.

|

|         load-module module-native-protocol-tcp auth-ip-acl=127.0.0.1 auth-anonymous=1

|

|________________________________________________________________________________________

|

|         we have to edit daemon file.

|

|         nano $PREFIX/etc/pulse/daemon.conf

|

|         change  exit-idle-time = 20 to  -1

|         restart termux


|________________________________________________________________________________________
